planID.title: Plan Identifier
planID.description: Unique identifier for the plan enrolled in by the member.

isActive.title: Is Active
isActive.description: Boolean flag indicates whether the plan is active.

isDependent.title: Is Dependent
isDependent.description: Indicates whether this member is a dependent.

primaryMemberID.title: Primary Member ID
primaryMemberID.description: Unique identifier of the primary subscriber if the member is a dependent.

beneficiaryRelationship.title: Beneficiary Relationship
beneficiaryRelationship.description: Beneficiary relationship to the subscriber if the member is a dependent (self, spouse, child, etc).

billingAccountID.title: Billing Account ID
billingAccountID.description: Unique identifier of the billing account.
